e in a callback function when external state changes.\n\nCalling setState synchronously within an effect body causes cascading renders that can hurt performance, and is not recommended. (https://react.dev/learn/you-might-not-need-an-effect).\n\n/Users/macbook/github code/Nabu/src/renderer/src/features/search/SearchPanel.tsx:130:7\n  128 |   useEffect(() => {\n  129 |     if (query.trim()) {\n> 130 |       performSearch(query)\n      |       ^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Avoid calling setState() directly within an effect\n  131 |     }\n  132 |     // Only run on mount — query changes via input are handled by the debounce\n  133 |     // eslint-disable-next-line react-hooks/exhaustive-deps","React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'performSearch' and 'query'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["1729"],["1730"],"'featureToggles' is assigned a value but never used.","'toggleErrors' is assigned a value but never used.","'dictationModel' is assigned a value but never used.","'setDictationModel' is assigned a value but never used.","'dictationModelStatus' is assigned a value but never used.","'setDictationModelStatus' is assigned a value but never used.","'dictationAvailable' is assigned a value but never used.","'_setDictationAvailable' is assigned a value but never used.","'dictationError' is assigned a value but never used.","'setDictationError' is assigned a value but never used.","'widgetShortcut' is assigned a value but never used.","'handleThemeChange' is assigned a value but never used.","'handleFeatureToggle' is assigned a value but never used.","'handleStartCapture' is assigned a value but never used.","'handleCaptureKeydown' is assigned a value but never used.","'handleResetShortcut' is assigned a value but never used.","@typescript-eslint/no-explicit-any","Unexpected any. Specify a different type.","TSAnyKeyword","unexpectedAny",["1731","1732"],"react-hooks/rules-of-hooks","React Hook \"useMemo\" is called conditionally. React Hooks must be called in